---
layout: layout.njk
title: Home
description: Daily reports on crypto movers with latest news and market context.
permalink: /index.html
---

<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Daily Crypto Movers</p>
  <h1>Why a coin pumped yesterday</h1>
  <p class="hero-text">
    Daily reports covering one major crypto mover, including market activity, possible reasons, and related news.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="button" href="/reports/{{ featuredReport.slug }}/">Read latest report</a>
    <a class="button secondary" href="/reports/">View all reports</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Latest Report</h2>
  {% set report = featuredReport %}
  {% include "report-card.njk" %}
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Recent Reports</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    {% for report in reports %}
      {% include "report-card.njk" %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
